  OneBodyOperator op_ob_angmom = {dim: 3, opt: 1, par: NULL, me: ob_angmom};
  int A=Q->A;
  complex double angmommes[A*A][3];
  complex double *j2mes = mes;

  calcSlaterDetOBHFMEs(Q, X, &op_ob_angmom, angmommes);

  int k,m;
  for (m=0; m<A; m++)
